<center><font face='arial'><br><br>





 <h2>Hunting the Oasis of Marr</h2><br><br><br>For Mages the Oasis of Marr is a great hunting zone. Depending on your level, crocs and snakes are great kills. If your a good mage you can solo yellows, even reds if you play it right, and the exp is fantastic.<br><br>One important thing to remember, is to use your water pet when fighting snakes, as its immune to their poison (one of their main ways of killing), so will take much less damage, your other pets will all just get eaten.<br><br><br>Also, there are a few hazards to watch out for, Sand Giants sometimes rome this zone, and they can really hurt, and drybone skeletons can really get annoying. There are no amazingly safe places to hunt, although your slightly better off near the water.<br><br><br><br></center><b><u>Zone Information:</u></b><br><br>Zonelookup Failed!